    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="what-is-a-good-domain-authority-score"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No universal "good" DA score exists. The metric only matters relative to your competitors. A DA of 35 is strong if your top 5 competitors average DA 25. That same DA 35 is weak if competitors average DA 55.</p></div></div>
