    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="what-tools-measure-page-authority-and-domain-autho"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Moz Link Explorer is the primary tool for both PA and DA scores. The MozBar browser extension shows PA and DA in search results. Ahrefs offers similar metrics called URL Rating (UR) and Domain Rating (DR). Semrush provides Authority Score at both the domain and page level.</p></div></div>
