<h2>Final Takeaway</h2>
<p>Page authority and domain authority measure different things. DA evaluates your entire site. PA evaluates a single URL. Both are Moz predictions, not Google ranking factors.</p>
<p>The smartest approach is building links to your highest-priority pages. This lifts PA for those specific URLs and compounds into higher DA over time. Stop chasing a vanity number. Start building authority where it drives revenue.</p>
